{
  "texts": [
    "These hash values are compared further to evaluate the difference between generated and real images.",
    "The generated image-segmentation pair is evaluated in data augmentation for the segmentation task.",
    "The U-Net is trained on 30 real and 120 generated images.",
    "The lowest Hausdorff distance of 7.2885 has been observed as compared to the results when U-Net trained on only real images or only generated images.",
    "However, the authors concluded that a mild form of mode collapse occurred which resulted in less diverse images."
  ]
}